Package: MotifStats
Title: Uncover the relationship between peaks and motifs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
  person(given = "Thomas", family = "Roberts", 
	email = "tomroberts.work15@gmail.com", 
	role = c("aut", "cre"),
	comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-6244-8670"))
Description: The performance of a peak calling experiment can be evaluated by 
  comparing the locations of peaks and canonical motifs. This package calculates 
  metrics to quantify the relationship between peaks and motifs, outputting
  an HTML report with the results.
URL: https://github.com/Tomrrr1/MotifStats
